<Placemark>
<name>Day 1: Keflavík → Reykjavík → Grundarfjörður</name>
<description>Keflavík → Reykjavík → Grundarfjörður | approx 245 km | Sleep: Grundarfjörður / Snæfellsnes campsite area | Pick up the Land Cruiser, visit Reykjavík, then drive to Kirkjufell country for the first night.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
-22.6056,63.985,0
-21.9426,64.1466,0
-21.9206,64.5383,0
-23.311,64.926,0
</coordinates></LineString>
</Placemark>


<Placemark>
<name>Day 2: Snæfellsnes loop → Hvammstangi</name>
<description>Snæfellsnes loop → Hvammstangi | approx 350 km | Sleep: Hvammstangi campsite area | Full Snæfellsnes day: coast, lava fields, black-pebble beach, sea cliffs, then reposition north.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
-23.311,64.926,0
