-23.3844,64.8208,0
-21.9206,64.5383,0
-20.9416,65.3975,0
</coordinates></LineString>
</Placemark>


<Placemark>
<name>Day 3: North Iceland to Akureyri, Goðafoss &amp; Mývatn</name>
<description>North Iceland to Akureyri, Goðafoss &amp; Mývatn | approx 330 km | Sleep: Mývatn / Reykjahlíð campsite area | Optional early Hvítserkur detour, then Akureyri, Goðafoss and the Mývatn area.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
-20.9416,65.3975,0
-20.6356,65.6065,0
