-16.9129,65.6426,0
</coordinates></LineString>
</Placemark>


<Placemark>
<name>Day 4: Mývatn sights → Dettifoss → Egilsstaðir / Seyðisfjörður</name>
<description>Mývatn sights → Dettifoss → Egilsstaðir / Seyðisfjörður | approx 285 km | Sleep: Seyðisfjörður or Egilsstaðir campsite area | Geothermal stops first, then Dettifoss and the scenic mountain road into Seyðisfjörður if conditions allow.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
-16.9129,65.6426,0
