</Placemark>


<Placemark>
<name>Day 5: Eastfjords → Höfn / Vestrahorn</name>
<description>Eastfjords → Höfn / Vestrahorn | approx 320 km | Sleep: Höfn campsite area | Slow fjord driving day. Aim for Höfn, with Stokksnes/Vestrahorn as the late-day photo stop.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
