</Placemark>


<Placemark>
<name>Day 6: Glacier lagoon → Skaftafell → Vík</name>
<description>Glacier lagoon → Skaftafell → Vík | approx 290 km | Sleep: Vík campsite area | Jökulsárlón and Diamond Beach early, then Skaftafell and the canyon before Vík.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
-15.202,64.2497,0
-16.1791,64.0476,0
