-18.1719,63.7714,0
-19.006,63.4186,0
</coordinates></LineString>
</Placemark>


<Placemark>
<name>Day 7: South Coast waterfalls → Geysir area</name>
<description>South Coast waterfalls → Geysir area | approx 230 km | Sleep: Geysir / Haukadalur campsite area | Black-sand beach safety day, then the classic South Coast waterfalls and a Golden Circle positioning night.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
-19.006,63.4186,0
