</coordinates></LineString>
</Placemark>


<Placemark>
<name>Day 8: Golden Circle → Keflavík return</name>
<description>Golden Circle → Keflavík return | approx 210 km | Sleep: Return / drop-off | Finish with Gullfoss, Geysir and Þingvellir, then return the car at Keflavík.</description>
<styleUrl>#routeStyle</styleUrl>
<LineString><tessellate>1</tessellate><coordinates>
